\begin_layout Subsection
Wavelength bands
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We should discuss the wavelength bands that interest us in this work: u
 (ultraviolet), g (green), r (red), i (near infrared), z (infrared), y (infrared
).
 Each band has a different range and a diffrerent midpoint value.
 The bands mostly don't overlap.
\end_layout

